<view class="profile-page">
  <view class="profile-hero">
    <view class="hero-user">
      <view class="avatar-wrap" aria-hidden="true">
        <image class="avatar-icon" src="/assets/profile/profile-user.svg" mode="aspectFit"></image>
      </view>
      <view class="user-copy">
        <text class="user-name">{{user.nickname}}</text>
        <view class="user-subtitle-row">
          <text class="online-dot"></text>
          <text class="user-subtitle">{{user.subtitle}}</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="profile-shell">
    <view class="record-card ds-card ds-card-elevated">
      <view class="card-title-row">
        <image class="card-title-icon" src="/assets/profile/profile-trophy.svg" mode="aspectFit"></image>
        <text class="card-title">我的战绩</text>
      </view>

      <view class="profile-stat-grid">
        <view wx:for="{{stats}}" wx:key="label" class="profile-stat-box">
          <view class="profile-stat-label-row">
            <view class="profile-stat-icon {{item.iconClass}}">
              <image class="profile-stat-icon-img" src="{{item.iconSrc}}" mode="aspectFit"></image>
            </view>
            <text class="profile-stat-label">{{item.label}}</text>
          </view>
          <view class="profile-stat-value-row">
            <text class="profile-stat-value">{{item.value}}</text>
            <text wx:if="{{item.unit}}" class="profile-stat-unit">{{item.unit}}</text>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="info-card index-card" bindtap="onOpenPlayIndexInfo">
      <image class="index-question-watermark" src="/assets/profile/profile-index-question.svg" mode="aspectFit"></image>
      <view class="card-title-row">
        <image class="card-title-icon card-title-icon-question" src="/assets/profile/profile-index-question-title.svg" mode="aspectFit"></image>
        <text class="card-title">白玩指数是什么？</text>
      </view>
      <text class="info-main">100 表示基本回本，超过 100 表示倒赚。</text>
      <text class="info-main">指数越高，说明这款实体游戏玩得越划算。</text>
      <view class="example-box">
        <image class="example-icon" src="/assets/profile/profile-example-fire.svg" mode="aspectFit"></image>
        <text class="example-text">示例：买入 ￥260，卖出回血 ￥250，白玩指数 96，几乎白玩。</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="info-card about-card">
      <view class="card-title-row">
        <image class="card-title-icon" src="/assets/profile/profile-about-info.svg" mode="aspectFit"></image>
        <text class="card-title">关于白玩计划</text>
      </view>
      <text class="about-copy">白玩计划是一个实体游戏买卖回血账本，帮你记录买游戏花了多少、卖游戏回了多少，以及哪些游戏实现了白玩。</text>
      <view class="about-note">
        <view class="note-line">
          <text class="note-dot"></text>
          <text>数字版游戏可以记录，但不参与回血和白玩统计。</text>
        </view>
        <view class="note-line">
          <text class="note-dot"></text>
          <text>当前版本暂不接入二手市场价格。</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="profile-links">
      <view
        wx:for="{{links}}"
        wx:key="label"
        class="profile-link"
        data-action="{{item.action}}"
        hover-class="profile-link-hover"
        hover-stay-time="120"
        bindtap="onOpenLink"
      >
        <text class="profile-link-label">{{item.label}}</text>
        <view class="profile-link-right">
          <text wx:if="{{item.value}}" class="profile-link-value">{{item.value}}</text>
          <image class="profile-link-icon" src="/assets/profile/profile-link-gamepad.svg" mode="aspectFit"></image>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
